**who —** Metafight — 超惑星戦記メタファイト — Chō Wakusei Senki Metafight (Sunsoft, Japan 1988) — the original Blaster Master is the localization of: an interstellar war whose hero is Kane Gardner, no boy and no frog. The twist: in Metafight, 'Sophia the 3rd' is the name of the PLANET — the US localization repurposed it as the name of Jason's tank

